## Testing the API

Test the API is working with cURL:

```bash
# Create a task
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"title":"Test Task","due_date":"2026-04-01","priority":"high"}'

# List tasks
curl http://localhost:8000/api/v1/tasks
```

